Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:41.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\pos(1450,1050)}故作坚强的表面之下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.93,0:22:45.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\pos(1450,1050)}{\fad(520,0)}压抑着破帛的悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:51.57,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(0,300)}在此招手示意 上台起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:56.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(0,520)}悬在空中 身影摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:59.12,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就此做结吧
